%span#nav_help.tl_helptext Help
%span#nav_tip{:style => "display: none"}
  To browse events in your Timeline, hold your mouse over the icons for a preview.  
  %br
  Click the icons for full details, or click an individual item inside the preview window.
  %br
  To navigate the Timeline: Drag it left or right, use the mouse scroll wheel, or the arrow keys, or double click on a date.
  
:javascript
  new Tip($('nav_help'), $('nav_tip'), {
    title: 'Timeline Help',
    width: '400px',
    border: 6,
    borderColor: '#74C5FF',
    fixed: true,
    hideOthers: true,
    viewport: true,
    showOn: 'click',
    hideOn: { element: 'closeButton', event: 'click' },
    stem: 'bottomRight',
    hook: {
      target: 'topLeft',
      tip: 'bottomRight'
    }
  });